This directory should contain all input datasets used for training, validation, and testing.
Recommended subfolders:

data/
├── train/
│   ├── 0/     # Class 0 (Reactive Follicular Hyperplasia)
│   └── 1/     # Class 1 (Follicular Lymphoma)
├── val/
│   ├── 0/
│   └── 1/
├── test/
│   ├── 0/
│   └── 1/
└── clinical_data/
    ├── clinical_data_train.xlsx
    ├── clinical_data_val.xlsx
    └── clinical_data_test.xlsx


Each .xlsx file must include:

CaseID — unique patient identifier

Classe — class label (0 = RFH, 1 = FL)

Clinical variables (e.g., Age, Sex, Location, etc.)

Morphometric nuclear features (e.g., Area, Eccentricity, MeanIntensity, etc.)
